import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react';
import {
  Container,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  Box,
  Button,
  Chip,
  Paper,
  IconButton,
  Tooltip,
} from '@mui/material';
import {
  Security,
  CloudUpload,
  Scanner,
  Shield,
  Analytics,
  Speed,
  AutoFixHigh,
  Assessment,
  Visibility,
  Download,
  Terminal,
  Settings,
  ContentCopy,
  GitHub,
  Storage,
} from '@mui/icons-material';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';

const Dashboard: React.FC = () => {
  const navigate = useNavigate();
  const [copiedCommand, setCopiedCommand] = useState('');

  const copyToClipboard = (text: string, command: string) => {
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
    setCopiedCommand(command);
    setTimeout(() => setCopiedCommand(''), 2000);
  };

  const features = [
    {
      title: 'Smart Log Detective',
      description: 'Our AI buddy finds weird stuff in your AWS logs - like a digital Sherlock Holmes!',
      icon: <Analytics sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: '#ff4d4d' }} />,
      action: () => navigate('/logs'),
      actionText: 'Start Detecting!',
      highlights: ['5 Log Types', 'Real-time Magic', 'AI Detective'],
      rotation: '-2deg',
      bgColor: '#fff9c4' // Post-it yellow
    },
    {
      title: 'Code Security Scanner',
      description: 'Scans your Terraform like a security guard with 150+ rules - no bad code gets past!',
      icon: <Scanner sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: '#2d5da1' }} />,
      action: () => navigate('/scanner'),
      actionText: 'Scan My Code!',
      highlights: ['150+ Rules', 'Terraform Pro', 'Instant Results'],
      rotation: '1.5deg',
      bgColor: '#ffffff'
    },
    {
      title: 'Rule Generator Wizard',
      description: 'Creates security rules automatically and learns from you - like having a smart assistant!',
      icon: <AutoFixHigh sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: '#ff4d4d' }} />,
      action: () => navigate('/rules'),
      actionText: 'Manage Rules!',
      highlights: ['Auto-Magic Rules', 'Learns from You', 'Smart Assistant'],
      rotation: '-1deg',
      bgColor: '#ffffff'
    }
  ];

  const stats = [
    { label: 'AWS Services', value: '35+', icon: <Shield />, rotation: '2deg' },
    { label: 'Security Rules', value: '150+', icon: <Assessment />, rotation: '-1deg' },
    { label: 'Log Types', value: '5', icon: <Visibility />, rotation: '1.5deg' },
    { label: 'Speed', value: '<50ms', icon: <Speed />, rotation: '-2deg' }
  ];

  const installationMethods = [
    {
      title: 'Quick CLI Setup',
      icon: <Terminal sx={{ fontSize: 32, color: '#ff4d4d' }} />,
      commands: [
        { label: 'Install it!', command: 'pip install securon-cli', description: 'Get the CLI tool on your machine' },
        { label: 'Scan stuff!', command: 'securon scan file main.tf', description: 'Check your Terraform files' },
        { label: 'Find bugs!', command: 'securon logs analyze vpc-flow.json', description: 'Look for weird things in logs' }
      ],
      rotation: '1deg'
    },
    {
      title: 'Docker Magic',
      icon: <Storage sx={{ fontSize: 32, color: '#2d5da1' }} />,
      commands: [
        { label: 'Get the image', command: 'docker pull securon/platform:latest', description: 'Download our container' },
        { label: 'Run the scan', command: 'docker run -v $(pwd):/workspace securon/platform scan', description: 'Scan in a container' }
      ],
      rotation: '-1.5deg'
    },
    {
      title: 'CI/CD Automation',
      icon: <Settings sx={{ fontSize: 32, color: '#ff4d4d' }} />,
      commands: [
        { label: 'GitHub Setup', command: 'uses: securon/action@v1\nwith:\n  terraform-path: ./infrastructure', description: 'Add to your GitHub workflow' },
        { label: 'GitLab Setup', command: 'securon-scan:\n  script:\n    - securon scan file *.tf', description: 'Add to .gitlab-ci.yml' }
      ],
      rotation: '0.5deg'
    }
  ];

  return (
    <Box sx={{ minHeight: '100vh', position: 'relative' }}>
      <Container maxWidth="xl" sx={{ py: 0 }}>
        {/* Art Deco Hero Section */}
        <Fade in={visible} timeout={1000}>
          <Box sx={{ 
            textAlign: 'center', 
            py: 16,
            position: 'relative',
            background: `
              radial-gradient(circle at 50% 20%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
              linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05) 0%, transparent 100%)
            `,
            '&::before': {
              content: '""',
              position: 'absolute',
              top: 0,
              left: '50%',
              transform: 'translateX(-50%)',
              width: 200,
              height: 4,
              background: 'linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #D4AF37, transparent)',
            },
            '&::after': {
              content: '""',
              position: 'absolute',
              bottom: 0,
              left: '50%',
              transform: 'translateX(-50%)',
              width: 200,
              height: 4,
              background: 'linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #D4AF37, transparent)',
            }
          }}>
            {/* Decorative Corner Elements */}
            <Box
              sx={{
                position: 'absolute',
                top: 32,
                left: 32,
                width: 40,
                height: 40,
                borderTop: '3px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
                borderLeft: '3px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
              }}
            />
            <Box
              sx={{
                position: 'absolute',
                top: 32,
                right: 32,
                width: 40,
                height: 40,
                borderTop: '3px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
                borderRight: '3px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
              }}
            />
            <Box
              sx={{
                position: 'absolute',
                bottom: 32,
                left: 32,
                width: 40,
                height: 40,
                borderBottom: '3px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
                borderLeft: '3px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
              }}
            />
            <Box
              sx={{
                position: 'absolute',
                bottom: 32,
                right: 32,
                width: 40,
                height: 40,
                borderBottom: '3px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
                borderRight: '3px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
              }}
            />

            <Zoom in={visible} timeout={1200}>
              <Box sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
                {/* Art Deco Diamond Logo */}
                <Box
                  sx={{
                    width: 120,
                    height: 120,
                    backgroundColor: '#D4AF37',
                    transform: 'rotate(45deg)',
                    display: 'flex',
                    alignItems: 'center',
                    justifyContent: 'center',
                    mx: 'auto',
                    mb: 4,
                    position: 'relative',
                    boxShadow: '0 0 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
                    '&::before': {
                      content: '""',
                      position: 'absolute',
                      top: 8,
                      left: 8,
                      right: 8,
                      bottom: 8,
                      border: '2px solid #0A0A0A',
                    }
                  }}
                >
                  <Security 
                    sx={{ 
                      fontSize: 48, 
                      color: '#0A0A0A',
                      transform: 'rotate(-45deg)',
                    }} 
                  />
                </Box>
                
                <Typography 
                  variant="h1" 
                  component="h1" 
                  gutterBottom 
                  sx={{ 
                    fontSize: { xs: '3rem', md: '4.5rem' },
                    color: '#D4AF37',
                    textShadow: '0 0 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
                    mb: 2,
                  }}
                >
                  Securon Platform
                </Typography>
              </Box>
            </Zoom>
            
            <Slide direction="up" in={visible} timeout={1400}>
              <Typography 
                variant="h4" 
                sx={{ 
                  mb: 4, 
                  color: '#F2F0E4',
                  fontFamily: '"Marcellus", serif',
                  textTransform: 'uppercase',
                  letterSpacing: '0.1em',
                }}
              >
                Luxury Cloud Security
              </Typography>
            </Slide>
            
            <Slide direction="up" in={visible} timeout={1600}>
              <Typography 
                variant="h6" 
                sx={{ 
                  mb: 8, 
                  maxWidth: 800, 
                  mx: 'auto', 
                  color: '#888888',
                  lineHeight: 1.8,
                  fontSize: '1.25rem',
                }}
              >
                Sophisticated machine learning algorithms detect anomalies with theatrical precision. 
                Scan infrastructure configurations through our premium interface or integrate seamlessly into your development pipeline.
              </Typography>
            </Slide>
            
            <Slide direction="up" in={visible} timeout={1800}>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 4, justifyContent: 'center', flexWrap: 'wrap' }}>
                <Button
                  variant="contained"
                  size="large"
                  onClick={() => navigate('/logs')}
                  sx={{ 
                    px: 6, 
                    py: 2,
                    fontSize: '1.1rem',
                  }}
                >
                  Begin Analysis
                </Button>
                <Button
                  variant="outlined"
                  size="large"
                  onClick={() => document.getElementById('cli-section')?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' })}
                  sx={{ 
                    px: 6, 
                    py: 2,
                    fontSize: '1.1rem',
                  }}
                >
                  Download CLI
                </Button>
              </Box>
            </Slide>
          </Box>
        </Fade>

        {/* Art Deco Stats Section */}
        <Box sx={{ mb: 12, position: 'relative' }}>
          {/* Section Header with Decorative Lines */}
          <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', mb: 8 }}>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
              <Box sx={{ width: 80, height: 1, bgcolor: '#D4AF37', mr: 3 }} />
              <Typography 
                variant="h3" 
                sx={{ 
                  color: '#D4AF37',
                  textAlign: 'center',
                  position: 'relative',
                }}
              >
                Platform Metrics
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ width: 80, height: 1, bgcolor: '#D4AF37', ml: 3 }} />
            </Box>
            <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#888888', textTransform: 'uppercase', letterSpacing: '0.2em' }}>
              Excellence in Numbers
            </Typography>
          </Box>

          <Grid container spacing={6}>
            {stats.map((stat, index) => (
              <Grid item xs={6} md={3} key={index}>
                <Zoom in={visible} timeout={1000 + stat.delay}>
                  <Card 
                    sx={{ 
                      textAlign: 'center', 
                      p: 4,
                      height: '100%',
                      position: 'relative',
                      '&::before': {
                        content: `"${['I', 'II', 'III', 'IV'][index]}"`,
                        position: 'absolute',
                        top: 16,
                        right: 16,
                        fontSize: '1.5rem',
                        fontFamily: '"Marcellus", serif',
                        color: 'rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
                      }
                    }}
                  >
                    {/* Diamond Icon Container */}
                    <Box
                      sx={{
                        width: 80,
                        height: 80,
                        transform: 'rotate(45deg)',
                        backgroundColor: '#D4AF37',
                        display: 'flex',
                        alignItems: 'center',
                        justifyContent: 'center',
                        mx: 'auto',
                        mb: 3,
                        position: 'relative',
                        '&::before': {
                          content: '""',
                          position: 'absolute',
                          top: 4,
                          left: 4,
                          right: 4,
                          bottom: 4,
                          border: '1px solid #0A0A0A',
                        }
                      }}
                    >
                      {React.cloneElement(stat.icon, {
                        sx: { 
                          fontSize: 32, 
                          color: '#0A0A0A',
                          transform: 'rotate(-45deg)',
                        }
                      })}
                    </Box>
                    
                    <Typography 
                      variant="h2" 
                      sx={{ 
                        color: '#D4AF37', 
                        fontFamily: '"Marcellus", serif',
                        mb: 1,
                        textShadow: '0 0 10px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2)',
                      }}
                    >
                      {stat.value}
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography 
                      variant="body1" 
                      sx={{ 
                        color: '#F2F0E4',
                        textTransform: 'uppercase',
                        letterSpacing: '0.1em',
                        fontWeight: 500,
                      }}
                    >
                      {stat.label}
                    </Typography>
                  </Card>
                </Zoom>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        </Box>

        {/* Art Deco CLI Installation Section */}
        <Box id="cli-section" sx={{ mb: 12, position: 'relative' }}>
          <Fade in={visible} timeout={2000}>
            <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', mb: 8 }}>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                <Box sx={{ width: 80, height: 1, bgcolor: '#D4AF37', mr: 3 }} />
                <Typography variant="h3" sx={{ color: '#D4AF37' }}>
                  Local Installation
                </Typography>
                <Box sx={{ width: 80, height: 1, bgcolor: '#D4AF37', ml: 3 }} />
              </Box>
              <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#888888', textTransform: 'uppercase', letterSpacing: '0.2em' }}>
                Premium Command Line Interface
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Fade>
          
          <Grid container spacing={6}>
            {installationMethods.map((method, index) => (
              <Grid item xs={12} md={4} key={index}>
                <Slide direction="up" in={visible} timeout={2200 + index * 200}>
                  <Card 
                    sx={{ 
                      height: '100%',
                      position: 'relative',
                      '&::before': {
                        content: `"${['I', 'II', 'III'][index]}"`,
                        position: 'absolute',
                        top: 16,
                        right: 16,
                        fontSize: '2rem',
                        fontFamily: '"Marcellus", serif',
                        color: 'rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2)',
                      }
                    }}
                  >
                    <CardContent sx={{ p: 4 }}>
                      {/* Diamond Icon Header */}
                      <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 4 }}>
                        <Box
                          sx={{
                            width: 48,
                            height: 48,
                            transform: 'rotate(45deg)',
                            backgroundColor: '#D4AF37',
                            display: 'flex',
                            alignItems: 'center',
                            justifyContent: 'center',
                            mr: 3,
                            '&::before': {
                              content: '""',
                              position: 'absolute',
                              top: 2,
                              left: 2,
                              right: 2,
                              bottom: 2,
                              border: '1px solid #0A0A0A',
                            }
                          }}
                        >
                          {React.cloneElement(method.icon, {
                            sx: { 
                              fontSize: 24, 
                              color: '#0A0A0A',
                              transform: 'rotate(-45deg)',
                            }
                          })}
                        </Box>
                        <Typography 
                          variant="h5" 
                          sx={{ 
                            color: '#D4AF37',
                            fontFamily: '"Marcellus", serif',
                            textTransform: 'uppercase',
                            letterSpacing: '0.1em',
                          }}
                        >
                          {method.title}
                        </Typography>
                      </Box>
                      
                      <List dense sx={{ '& .MuiListItem-root': { px: 0, py: 2 } }}>
                        {method.commands.map((cmd, idx) => (
                          <ListItem key={idx}>
                            <Box sx={{ width: '100%' }}>
                              <Typography 
                                variant="subtitle2" 
                                sx={{ 
                                  color: '#D4AF37', 
                                  fontWeight: 600, 
                                  mb: 1,
                                  textTransform: 'uppercase',
                                  letterSpacing: '0.05em',
                                }}
                              >
                                {cmd.label}
                              </Typography>
                              <Paper 
                                sx={{ 
                                  p: 3, 
                                  bgcolor: '#0A0A0A', 
                                  border: '1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
                                  borderRadius: 0,
                                  position: 'relative',
                                  '&:hover': { 
                                    borderColor: '#D4AF37',
                                    boxShadow: '0 0 10px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2)',
                                  },
                                  transition: 'all 0.3s ease'
                                }}
                              >
                                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'flex-start' }}>
                                  <Typography 
                                    component="pre" 
                                    sx={{ 
                                      color: '#D4AF37', 
                                      fontFamily: '"Courier New", monospace',
                                      fontSize: '0.9rem', 
                                      margin: 0, 
                                      whiteSpace: 'pre-wrap',
                                      lineHeight: 1.4,
                                    }}
                                  >
                                    {cmd.command}
                                  </Typography>
                                  <Tooltip title={copiedCommand === cmd.command ? 'Copied!' : 'Copy Command'}>
                                    <IconButton
                                      size="small"
                                      onClick={() => copyToClipboard(cmd.command, cmd.command)}
                                      sx={{ 
                                        color: copiedCommand === cmd.command ? '#4CAF50' : '#D4AF37', 
                                        ml: 2,
                                        '&:hover': {
                                          backgroundColor: 'rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1)',
                                        }
                                      }}
                                    >
                                      <ContentCopy fontSize="small" />
                                    </IconButton>
                                  </Tooltip>
                                </Box>
                              </Paper>
                              <Typography 
                                variant="body2" 
                                sx={{ 
                                  mt: 1, 
                                  color: '#888888',
                                  fontStyle: 'italic',
                                }}
                              >
                                {cmd.description}
                              </Typography>
                            </Box>
                          </ListItem>
                        ))}
                      </List>
                    </CardContent>
                  </Card>
                </Slide>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        </Box>

        {/* Art Deco CI/CD Integration Steps */}
        <Fade in={visible} timeout={2800}>
          <Box 
            sx={{ 
              p: 8, 
              mb: 12, 
              position: 'relative',
              border: '2px solid #D4AF37',
              '&::before': {
                content: '""',
                position: 'absolute',
                top: -2,
                left: 40,
                right: 40,
                height: 2,
                backgroundColor: '#0A0A0A',
              },
              '&::after': {
                content: '""',
                position: 'absolute',
                bottom: -2,
                left: 40,
                right: 40,
                height: 2,
                backgroundColor: '#0A0A0A',
              }
            }}
          >
            {/* Section Header */}
            <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', mb: 8 }}>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                <Box sx={{ width: 80, height: 1, bgcolor: '#D4AF37', mr: 3 }} />
                <Typography variant="h3" sx={{ color: '#D4AF37' }}>
                  Pipeline Integration
                </Typography>
                <Box sx={{ width: 80, height: 1, bgcolor: '#D4AF37', ml: 3 }} />
              </Box>
              <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#888888', textTransform: 'uppercase', letterSpacing: '0.2em' }}>
                Automated Security Excellence
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            
            <Grid container spacing={6}>
              {cicdSteps.map((step, index) => (
                <Grid item xs={12} md={3} key={index}>
                  <Zoom in={visible} timeout={3000 + index * 200}>
                    <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', position: 'relative' }}>
                      {/* Roman Numeral in Corner */}
                      <Typography
                        sx={{
                          position: 'absolute',
                          top: -10,
                          right: 0,
                          fontSize: '3rem',
                          fontFamily: '"Marcellus", serif',
                          color: 'rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2)',
                          lineHeight: 1,
                        }}
                      >
                        {['I', 'II', 'III', 'IV'][index]}
                      </Typography>
                      
                      {/* Diamond Step Container */}
                      <Box
                        sx={{
                          width: 100,
                          height: 100,
                          transform: 'rotate(45deg)',
                          backgroundColor: '#D4AF37',
                          display: 'flex',
                          alignItems: 'center',
                          justifyContent: 'center',
                          mx: 'auto',
                          mb: 4,
                          position: 'relative',
                          boxShadow: '0 0 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
                          '&::before': {
                            content: '""',
                            position: 'absolute',
                            top: 6,
                            left: 6,
                            right: 6,
                            bottom: 6,
                            border: '2px solid #0A0A0A',
                          }
                        }}
                      >
                        <Typography
                          sx={{
                            fontSize: '2rem',
                            fontFamily: '"Marcellus", serif',
                            color: '#0A0A0A',
                            transform: 'rotate(-45deg)',
                            fontWeight: 'bold',
                          }}
                        >
                          {step.step}
                        </Typography>
                      </Box>
                      
                      {/* Icon */}
                      <Box sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                        {React.cloneElement(step.icon, { 
                          sx: { 
                            fontSize: 48, 
                            color: '#D4AF37',
                          } 
                        })}
                      </Box>
                      
                      <Typography 
                        variant="h5" 
                        gutterBottom 
                        sx={{ 
                          color: '#D4AF37',
                          fontFamily: '"Marcellus", serif',
                          textTransform: 'uppercase',
                          letterSpacing: '0.1em',
                          mb: 2,
                        }}
                      >
                        {step.title}
                      </Typography>
                      <Typography 
                        variant="body1" 
                        sx={{ 
                          color: '#888888',
                          lineHeight: 1.6,
                        }}
                      >
                        {step.description}
                      </Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Zoom>
                </Grid>
              ))}
            </Grid>
            
            {/* Platform Integration */}
            <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', mt: 8 }}>
              <Typography 
                variant="h5" 
                sx={{ 
                  mb: 4, 
                  color: '#D4AF37',
                  fontFamily: '"Marcellus", serif',
                  textTransform: 'uppercase',
                  letterSpacing: '0.1em',
                }}
              >
                Supported Platforms
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 3, justifyContent: 'center', flexWrap: 'wrap' }}>
                {[
                  { icon: <GitHub />, label: 'GitHub Actions' },
                  { icon: <Code />, label: 'GitLab CI' },
                  { icon: <Build />, label: 'Jenkins' },
                  { icon: <CloudDownload />, label: 'Azure DevOps' }
                ].map((platform, index) => (
                  <Chip 
                    key={index}
                    icon={platform.icon} 
                    label={platform.label} 
                    variant="outlined" 
                    sx={{ 
                      borderColor: '#D4AF37', 
                      color: '#D4AF37',
                      backgroundColor: 'transparent',
                      borderRadius: 0,
                      px: 2,
                      py: 1,
                      fontSize: '1rem',
                      '&:hover': {
                        backgroundColor: 'rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1)',
                        borderColor: '#F2E8C4',
                      },
                      transition: 'all 0.3s ease',
                    }} 
                  />
                ))}
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Fade>

        {/* Art Deco Core Features */}
        <Box sx={{ mb: 12 }}>
          <Fade in={visible} timeout={3400}>
            <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', mb: 8 }}>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                <Box sx={{ width: 80, height: 1, bgcolor: '#D4AF37', mr: 3 }} />
                <Typography variant="h3" sx={{ color: '#D4AF37' }}>
                  Security Features
                </Typography>
                <Box sx={{ width: 80, height: 1, bgcolor: '#D4AF37', ml: 3 }} />
              </Box>
              <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#888888', textTransform: 'uppercase', letterSpacing: '0.2em' }}>
                Architectural Excellence
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Fade>
          
          <Grid container spacing={6}>
            {features.map((feature, index) => (
              <Grid item xs={12} md={4} key={index}>
                <Slide direction="up" in={visible} timeout={3600 + feature.delay}>
                  <Card 
                    sx={{ 
                      height: '100%', 
                      display: 'flex', 
                      flexDirection: 'column',
                      position: 'relative',
                      '&::before': {
                        content: `"${['I', 'II', 'III'][index]}"`,
                        position: 'absolute',
                        top: 16,
                        right: 16,
                        fontSize: '2rem',
                        fontFamily: '"Marcellus", serif',
                        color: 'rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2)',
                      }
                    }}
                  >
                    <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1, textAlign: 'center', p: 6 }}>
                      {/* Diamond Icon Container */}
                      <Box
                        sx={{
                          width: 80,
                          height: 80,
                          transform: 'rotate(45deg)',
                          backgroundColor: '#D4AF37',
                          display: 'flex',
                          alignItems: 'center',
                          justifyContent: 'center',
                          mx: 'auto',
                          mb: 4,
                          position: 'relative',
                          '&::before': {
                            content: '""',
                            position: 'absolute',
                            top: 4,
                            left: 4,
                            right: 4,
                            bottom: 4,
                            border: '1px solid #0A0A0A',
                          }
                        }}
                      >
                        {React.cloneElement(feature.icon, {
                          sx: { 
                            fontSize: 32, 
                            color: '#0A0A0A',
                            transform: 'rotate(-45deg)',
                          }
                        })}
                      </Box>
                      
                      <Typography 
                        variant="h4" 
                        component="h3" 
                        gutterBottom 
                        sx={{ 
                          color: '#D4AF37',
                          fontFamily: '"Marcellus", serif',
                          textTransform: 'uppercase',
                          letterSpacing: '0.1em',
                          mb: 3,
                        }}
                      >
                        {feature.title}
                      </Typography>
                      
                      <Typography 
                        variant="body1" 
                        sx={{ 
                          mb: 4, 
                          lineHeight: 1.8,
                          color: '#F2F0E4',
                        }}
                      >
                        {feature.description}
                      </Typography>
                      
                      <Box sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
                        {feature.highlights.map((highlight, idx) => (
                          <Chip 
                            key={idx}
                            label={highlight} 
                            size="small" 
                            variant="outlined" 
                            sx={{ 
                              m: 0.5, 
                              borderColor: '#D4AF37', 
                              color: '#D4AF37',
                              backgroundColor: 'transparent',
                              borderRadius: 0,
                              '&:hover': { 
                                backgroundColor: 'rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1)',
                              },
                              transition: 'all 0.3s ease',
                            }}
                          />
                        ))}
                      </Box>
                      
                      <Button
                        variant="contained"
                        fullWidth
                        onClick={feature.action}
                        sx={{ 
                          mt: 'auto',
                          py: 2,
                          fontSize: '1.1rem',
                        }}
                      >
                        {feature.actionText}
                      </Button>
                    </CardContent>
                  </Card>
                </Slide>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        </Box>

        {/* Art Deco Call to Action */}
        <Fade in={visible} timeout={4200}>
          <Box 
            sx={{ 
              textAlign: 'center', 
              py: 12, 
              mb: 8,
              position: 'relative',
              border: '3px solid #D4AF37',
              '&::before': {
                content: '""',
                position: 'absolute',
                top: -3,
                left: 60,
                right: 60,
                height: 3,
                backgroundColor: '#0A0A0A',
              },
              '&::after': {
                content: '""',
                position: 'absolute',
                bottom: -3,
                left: 60,
                right: 60,
                height: 3,
                backgroundColor: '#0A0A0A',
              }
            }}
          >
            {/* Decorative Corner Elements */}
            <Box
              sx={{
                position: 'absolute',
                top: 16,
                left: 16,
                width: 40,
                height: 40,
                borderTop: '3px solid #D4AF37',
                borderLeft: '3px solid #D4AF37',
              }}
            />
            <Box
              sx={{
                position: 'absolute',
                top: 16,
                right: 16,
                width: 40,
                height: 40,
                borderTop: '3px solid #D4AF37',
                borderRight: '3px solid #D4AF37',
              }}
            />
            <Box
              sx={{
                position: 'absolute',
                bottom: 16,
                left: 16,
                width: 40,
                height: 40,
                borderBottom: '3px solid #D4AF37',
                borderLeft: '3px solid #D4AF37',
              }}
            />
            <Box
              sx={{
                position: 'absolute',
                bottom: 16,
                right: 16,
                width: 40,
                height: 40,
                borderBottom: '3px solid #D4AF37',
                borderRight: '3px solid #D4AF37',
              }}
            />

            <Typography 
              variant="h2" 
              gutterBottom 
              sx={{ 
                color: '#D4AF37',
                mb: 4,
                textShadow: '0 0 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3)',
              }}
            >
              Begin Your Security Journey
            </Typography>
            <Typography 
              variant="h5" 
              sx={{ 
                mb: 6, 
                maxWidth: 800, 
                mx: 'auto',
                color: '#888888',
                lineHeight: 1.6,
              }}
            >
              Experience premium cloud security through our sophisticated interface, 
              command-line tools, or seamless pipeline integration.
            </Typography>
            
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 4, justifyContent: 'center', flexWrap: 'wrap' }}>
              <Button
                variant="contained"
                size="large"
                onClick={() => navigate('/logs')}
                sx={{ 
                  px: 6, 
                  py: 2,
                  fontSize: '1.1rem',
                }}
              >
                Analyze Logs
              </Button>
              <Button
                variant="outlined"
                size="large"
                onClick={() => navigate('/scanner')}
                sx={{ 
                  px: 6, 
                  py: 2,
                  fontSize: '1.1rem',
                }}
              >
                Scan Infrastructure
              </Button>
              <Button
                variant="outlined"
                size="large"
                onClick={() => document.getElementById('cli-section')?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' })}
                sx={{ 
                  px: 6, 
                  py: 2,
                  fontSize: '1.1rem',
                }}
              >
                Download CLI
              </Button>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Fade>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Dashboard;
